            <tr style="background: rgba(196,43,43,0.15);">
                <th style="padding: 14px 16px; text-align: left; color: #fff; font-weight: 700;">#</th>
                <th style="padding: 14px 16px; text-align: left; color: #fff; font-weight: 700;">Ошибка</th>
                <th style="padding: 14px 16px; text-align: left; color: #fff; font-weight: 700;">Последствие</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            <tr><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">1</td><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">Зарплата ниже рынка + штрафы</td><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">Текучка 50-60%/год, лучшие уходят первыми</td></tr>
            <tr><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">2</td><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">KPI на 15 показателей</td><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">Сотрудник не может посчитать зарплату → демотивация</td></tr>
            <tr><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">3</td><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">Нет описанных инструкций</td><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">Каждый новый сотрудник «изобретает велосипед»</td></tr>
            <tr><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">4</td><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">Найм без проверки ценностей</td><td style="padding: 12px 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05);">Токсичный сотрудник разрушает культуру за месяц</td></tr>
